+- area: udp
+  change: |
+    Fixed UDP proxy filter crash when a cluster is updated via CDS (e.g., on ``HostSet`` changes).
+    Previously, ``onClusterAddOrUpdate()`` used ``emplace()`` which silently failed when updating an existing
+    cluster, leaving a stale ``ClusterInfo`` object with dangling pointers. Now uses ``insert_or_assign()``
+    to correctly replace cluster info on updates.
 
